.SH DESCRIPTION

.B port-install-build-deps
determines the BUILD_DEPENDS for the port in the current
working directory using
.B make build-depends-list
and attempts to install all build dependencies using pkg.
This significantly reduces the time required for a build
in the event that not all dependencies are installed.

.SH RETURN VALUES

0 on success, non-zero error codes otherwise

